  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n84/mode/1up">81</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n85/mode/1up">82</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. atuveṉap peyar koṭuttōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiccol āṟāvatām. atu uṭaiyatāy niṟkuntaṉṉāṉum piṟitoṉṟāṉum itaṉatituveṉpatu paṭa niṟkumataṉāṟ kiḷaviyiṟṟōṉ ṟuṅkiḻamaiyaip poruḷākavuṭaittu. e-ṟu. eṉavē, āṟāvatu kiḻamaipporuṭṭeṉṟum, akkiḻamai taṉṉāṉ vanta taṟkiḻamaiyum piṟitāṉ vanta piṟitiṉkiḻamaiyumeṉa iraṇṭeṉṟuṅ kūṟiyavāṟām.</p>
<p>taṉṉeṉṟatu taṉṉōṭoṟṟumaiyuṭaiya poruḷai. piṟiteṉṟatu taṉṉiṉ vēṟākiya poruḷai.</p>
<p>aḵtēl, taṉṉiṉum piṟitiṉumākiya kiḻamaitteṉṉātu itaṉatituveṉu maṉṉakiḷavikkiḻamaitteṉṟateṉṉaiyeṉiṉ:- poruṭkiḻamaiyum, paṇpukkiḻamaiyum, toḻiṟkiḻamaiyum avaipōlavaṉavumeṉak kiḻamaitām pala, avaṟṟuḷoṉṟu cuṭṭātu itaṉatutiveṉṉuñcollāṟṟōṉṟuṅ kiḻamaimāttiram cuṭṭumeṉṟaṟku itaṉatitu veṉumaṉṉakiḷavikkiḻamaitteṉṟār.</p>
<p>itaṉavivaiyeṉṉum paṉmaiyuruputtoṭarumaṭaṅkutaṟku aṉṉakiḷaviyeṉṟār.</p>
<p>oṉṟu pala kuḻīiya taṟkiḻamaiyum, vēṟu pala kuḻīiya taṟkiḻamaiyum, oṉṟiyaṟkiḻamaiyum, uṟuppiṉkiḻamaiyum, meytirintāya taṟkiḻamaiyumeṉat taṟkiḻamai aintuvakaippaṭum.</p>
<p>poruḷiṉkiḻamaiyum, nilattiṉkiḻamaiyum, kālattiṉkiḻamaiyumeṉap piṟitiṉkiḻamai mūvakaippaṭum. avaṟṟiṟkutāraṇam muṉṉark kāṭṭutum.	(18)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/279/mode/1up">279</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/280/mode/1up">280</ref>.</p>
      <p>itu, muṟaiyāṉē āṟāvatu ipporuṭkaṇ varum eṉkiṉṟatu.</p>
<p>(i-ḷ.)atu eṉap peyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi āṟākuvatē- mēl atu eṉap peyar koṭuttuōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiccol āṟāvatām; atu- avvēṟṟumaiccol, taṉṉiṉum- oru poruḷiṉatu uṭaimaip poruḷāki niṟkum taṉṉōṭu oṟṟumaiyuṭaiya poruḷāṉum, piṟitiṉum- oruporuṉiṉatu uṭaimaip poruḷāy niṟkum taṉṉiṉ vēṟākiya poruḷāṉum, `itaṉatu itu' eṉṉum-`ipporuḷiṉuṭaiyatu ipporuḷ' eṉpatu paṭa niṟkum, aṉṉa kiḷavik kiḻamaittu- aṉṉa poruḷāl tōṉṟum kiḻamaiyaip poruḷāka uṭaittu(e-ṟu.)</p>
<p>īṇṭut `taṉ' eṉṟatu, urupu ēṟkum poruḷai.`aṉṉa'eṉṟār, `itaṉa ivai' eṉṉum paṉmai uṟupum, `ātu' eṉṉum orumai urupum aṭaṅkutaṟku.</p>
<p>(u-m.)cāttaṉa āṭai</p>
<p>taṉātu veḷvēl</p>
<p>(`yāṉai vaḷavaṉ kolli mīmicai')</p>
<p>eṉa varum.</p>
<p>oṉṟu pala kuḻīiyatum, vēṟu pala kuḻīiyatum,</p>
<p>oṉṟiyaṟkiḻamaiyum, uṟuppiṉ kiḻamaiyum,</p>
<p>mey tirintu āyatum eṉat taṟkiḻamai aintu vakaippaṭum,</p>
<p>`aimpāl urimaiyum ataṉtaṟ kiḻamai.'</p>
<p>eṉpatu akattiyam ātaliṉ.</p>
<p>poruḷiṉ kiḻamaiyum, nilattiṉ kiḻamaiyum, kālattiṉ kiḻamaiyum eṉap piṟitiṉ kiḻamai mūva kappaṭum.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC250-Nacc-cit1">
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
